name: Burger King
description: Well-known fast-food chain serving grilled burgers, fries & shakes.
address: Burger King, Pacific Link, 10355 120 St B, Surrey, BC V3V 0C1

detailed_reviews.review_text: Open 24 hours. Dependable option for those late night snacks/dinners. The staff is friendly and receptive to your requests. The food is good, and substantial. I dont like the fact that they charge you for zesty sauce (only one is free). Best onion rings. The veggie whopper (I get it without the patty), with added cheese is awesome.
Had the chicken sandwich combo and enjoyed it. The restsurant is clean, well lit and, well organized. Service was prompt & pleasant... Thank ubso much Shenazh...
Food is great and staff is friendly. Hard to find a fast food restaurant were staff is friendly and polite. Good job Burger King
The service was quick. Chicken Nuggets were good and not pricey
Drive through is quick compared to alot of places nearby, from my experiences there, the food is always fresh and tasty!
Drive through works fast,  but fries were barely warm.

From my perspective I love this place and they have very fast service of food. A lot of time I went to this restaurant and the staff welcomes me in very friendly way. And, I recommend all my friends to go in this restaurant to experience the same. Kid-friendliness: My little cousin always feels hungry and this restaurant is his favourite because the crew members talk to him as his friends and politely help him to give his first order.

Very special sauce policy. This made me laugh. The number one most important thing that they post in big bold letters in my face is how many sauces I get with each purchase. Obviously someone was abusing the sauces. How many people asked for two or three sauces well only getting a single order to encourage this sign to get made and posted so prominently? I love it!
So far i like this location. Not too busy, the food is prepared properly and not rushed. Service Crew are friendly and would advise you of any deals or promotion they have.

EDIT: I recently visited this place again and I was given very good customer service. That s how it s suppose to be. Girls working at night shift are doing an excellent job. Will definitely come back again. Food was good. The girl I dealt with had zero level of customer service. I asked for mayonnaise and her reaction was so bad that I felt so unwelcoming. If you see a brown dude ordering food that doesn t mean that you have to show us attitude. Plus, I was so nice to her and addressed her as MADAM. Management needs to solve this issue and ask their employees to be nice with the customers.

Order a whopper with cheese meal with an extra hot patty (which may have been cooked to order).  The burger was the best I have had at a fast food place in recent memory. Service was friendly and polite also.

Been here multiple times.  Service is slightly  slower compared to other locations.  But the quality and freshness is best. They cook to order so when you get it, it is piping hot.  Original chicken sandwich here is crispier than others.

detailed_reviews.review_text: Never had a problem here. Food is always standard, but what I love is that they let us order 200 nuggets without much more than a giggle. See the pictures below. What a fun time that was! Students, if you ever want to celebrate the end of exams this is a great, clean way to go. Your arteries sure wont be clean though.
Today we went Burger King for lunch. Staff was very friendly specially Dilpreet and parbhav. They helped us a lot. Thanks

99% of the time, they get my order right and charge correct amount for my orders. Only one time when I ordered, the staff incorrectly overcharged the order. Not sure if this was a new staff member but I pointed out the issue and it was resolved before I paid.  Best deal was the two Whoppers for $8.00 for the longest time and now it s two Whoppers for $9.00.  The staff are very friendly I would recommend this restaurant.
Excellent service , and very clean environment enjoyed my burger
It was good made it in and I got food quickly and it tasted good.
Really love the customer service representatives here, they are really nice and kind

Excellent service. Got my order wrong (Roadhouse King) and got a Garlic Roadhouse by accident. Let them know and they let me keep the first burger, gave me my correct replacement and got onion rings on the side free of charge to add to my first burger. Proper courtesy. Many thanks! Food was great, always order the same thing.
Kind staff! Great atmosphere. Fast and excellent service.

We like to grab a whopper cheese,  onion rings with spicy dip and hit a park in beach for some quiet hour.  This one was  in New West then we went to the Fraser river.   Food was fresh and hot.  Service friendly and fast.

When reviewing Burger King I believe most culinary critics only focus on quality which is only 1/3 of the equation. What about quantity and price? I can currently get 4 cheesy tots for one dollar! Thats unbelievable value. The deals at this place are awesome, the staff is nice and the burgers are pretty great too. Long live my second home, the home of the Whopper!

detailed_reviews.review_text: Food is really good, service was good and fast. Nice inside too. Easy 5 star
Friday evening is always hectic here but the girl at the front counter has always served us with a smile. I saw her bringing food for the disable man to his table even though he was so rude to her.

My first and second orders to go I was so disappointed by the service, that was a  shorter  Indian lady, she was not in mood to service, put attitude on customers even not give me any sauce for my chicken nugs and fresh fried. But when I came over again that was a taller Indian lady service me, she is very polite and kind, I come back here again and again because her and I decided giving 5 stars for her  thank you for your great service!
Easily the best and cleanest fast food place on sixth. The ladies that work the counter are great, they also dump extra fries into mybag. Easy choice to go here over websites or mcdicks.

detailed_reviews.review_text: French fries are delicious

The 2 for $8 deal is quite attractive; I can buy two Whoppers and an ice-cream cone for less than ten dollars. The Whoppers are juicy and taste good as usual; just the waiting time is a little bit longer, although there were already three staff working in the kitchen
They always make everything fresh here but for some reason theres always at least 1 homeless person that comes inside (which could ruin your dining experience)

GOOD DEAL ALERT! I found out they have this King Meal Deal for $4.99+tax that includes 2 (value-size) sandwiches, 1 small fries and a drink! You can choose 2 of 3 sandwiches: the chicken junior, the BK roundhouse (has fried onion rings in it), or regular cheeseburger. The fries came hot and fresh, some had a tougher outer skin though, but not a big deal. The staff made an effort to keep the tables clean. They also have a $1 soft serve deal right now! I didnt get one but I did notice that the size and shape was quite inconsistent between different employees making them; some very short and badly swirled whereas another employee made really pretty, tall swirls (even nicer than in the advertisements haha). Side note: washrooms need to be unlocked by employees at the cash.
Nice place. Always a good place to get your burger fix. Flame broiled, lesser greasy, clean restaurant, friendly service, good deals! Lots of parking, drive through.
